OL,3,CAll hantavirus passengers return home
OL,4,Cas cruise ship departs Canary Islands
OL,6,FAll of the passengers of the
OL,7,Fhantavirus-stricken cruise ship have
OL,8,Fnow disembarked and left Tenerife,
OL,9,Fwith flights to more than 20 countries
OL,10,Farranged and dozens in quarantine.
OL,12,FA French woman became the latest to be
OL,13,Fconfirmed as infected, while an
OL,14,FAmerican was suspected of infection
OL,15,Fafter initial testing.
OL,17,FPassengers began flying home aboard
OL,18,Fmilitary and government planes on
OL,19,FSunday after the MV Hondius anchored
OL,20,Fin the Canary Islands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
