CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778587868
OL,3,CAll hantavirus passengers return home
OL,4,Cas cruise ship departs Canary Islands
OL,6,FPersonnel in full-body protective gear
OL,7,Fand breathing masks escorted the
OL,8,Ftravellers from the ship to shore in
OL,9,FTenerife and onto an airport, with the
OL,10,Ffinal flight departing on Monday.
OL,12,F"If they stayed longer on the ship,
OL,13,Fthe situation could have been
OL,14,Fdifficult," said Tedros Adhanom
OL,15,FGhebreyesus, director-general of the
OL,16,FWorld Health Organization.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778587868
OL,3,CAll hantavirus passengers return home
OL,4,Cas cruise ship departs Canary Islands
OL,6,FHe said citizens of the countries that
OL,7,Fpassengers are returning to should
OL,8,Fknow "there is nothing to fear, the
OL,9,Frisk is low, this is not another
OL,10,FCovid."
OL,12,FThree cruise ship passengers have
OL,13,Fdied, and six people with confirmed or
OL,14,Fsuspected cases of hantavirus are
OL,15,Fbeing quarantined, according to the
OL,16,FWHO.
OL,18,FThe lab results of the American who
OL,19,Ftested positive were inconclusive, WHO
OL,20,Fspokesperson Sarah Tyler said on
OL,21,FMonday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
