PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778587868
OL,3,CAll hantavirus passengers return home
OL,4,Cas cruise ship departs Canary Islands
OL,6,FThe ship's captain, Jan Dobrogowski,
OL,7,Fissued a video message Monday praising
OL,8,Fpassengers and crew for their courage
OL,9,Fand perseverance. He also called for
OL,10,Frespect for their privacy.
OL,12,F"I could not imagine sailing through
OL,13,Fthese circumstances with a better
OL,14,Fgroup of people, guests and crew
OL,15,Falike," he said.
OL,17,FThe French woman who tested positive
OL,18,Ffor the hantavirus was in intensive
OL,19,Fcare in a stable condition at a Paris
OL,20,Fhospital, French Prime Minister
OL,21,FSebastien Lecornu said on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
