PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778587868
OL,3,CAll hantavirus passengers return home
OL,4,Cas cruise ship departs Canary Islands
OL,6,FHe said four French passengers who
OL,7,Freturned Sunday tested negative but
OL,8,Fremained in isolation at the same
OL,9,Fhospital.
OL,11,FOne of the 18 evacuated passengers
OL,12,Fflown to the US also tested positive
OL,13,Ffor the hantavirus but was not showing
OL,14,Fsymptoms, while another had mild
OL,15,Fsymptoms, US health officials said.
OL,17,FSouth African health authorities said
OL,18,Fon Monday that the condition of a
OL,19,FBritish man admitted to a hospital in
OL,20,FJohannesburg and being treated for
OL,21,Fhantavirus was gradually improving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
