OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778587868
OL,3,CAll hantavirus passengers return home
OL,4,Cas cruise ship departs Canary Islands
OL,6,FHe was evacuated from the ship on
OL,7,FApril 27 after becoming ill.
OL,9,FIn the UK, 20 British passengers from
OL,10,Fthe MV Hondius are isolating at Arrowe
OL,11,FPark Hospital on the Wirral after
OL,12,Farriving late on Sunday.
OL,14,FOne German national, who is a UK
OL,15,Fresident, and one Japanese passenger
OL,16,Fare also with them.
OL,18,FThey are expected to spend 45 days in
OL,19,Fself-isolation, and all of them are
OL,20,Fundergoing testing to see if they have
OL,21,Fany signs of hantavirus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
