OL,3,CAll hantavirus passengers return home
OL,4,Cas cruise ship departs Canary Islands
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the MV Hondius has departed
OL,7,Fthe Canary Islands on route to
OL,8,FRotterdam and is expected to arrive on
OL,9,FSunday. It still has 25 members of the
OL,10,Fcrew and two medical professionals on
OL,11,Fboard.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
